description: Gene expresion data from sample phc98074
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip HG-U133A Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 400.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 6 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GCS3000 high resolution scanner (M10).
